ENV PATH /root/.local/bin:$PATH

WORKDIR /code

ENV POETRY_VIRTUALENVS_CREATE false

RUN poetry install -vv --no-interaction --no-root --extras "developer pymagnitude"

ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
